OL,3,CWe've won against Haiti, let's beat
OL,4,CMorocco, Swinney says ahead of
OL,5,CScotland game
OL,7,FScotland has the "verve, energy and
OL,8,Fability" to beat Morocco as it heads
OL,9,Finto its second World Cup match, the
OL,10,Fcountry's First Minister has said.
OL,12,FJohn Swinney said he was confident
OL,13,FSteve Clarke's squad could defeat the
OL,14,FAfrican nation following its 1-0 win
OL,15,Fagainst Haiti in America.
OL,17,FHe predicted the men's national team
OL,18,Fwould beat Morocco 2-1 in Boston and
OL,19,Fmake it out of the group stages of the
OL,20,Ftournament.
OL,26,@oD@ROUpD@HO]
