OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781844476
OL,3,CWe've won against Haiti, let's beat
OL,4,CMorocco, Swinney says ahead of
OL,5,CScotland game
OL,7,FThe SNP leader also lauded the Tartan
OL,8,FArmy as "extraordinary advocates and
OL,9,Fambassadors" for Scotland.
OL,11,FThe country is currently at the top of
OL,12,Fits group after claiming its first
OL,13,FWorld Cup match win in 36 years.
OL,15,FSpeaking to the Press Association, Mr
OL,16,FSwinney delivered a message to the
OL,17,Fnational team ahead of their match on
OL,18,FFriday night.
OL,26,@pD@IOUqD@LO]
