OL,3,CWe've won against Haiti, let's beat
OL,4,CMorocco, Swinney says ahead of
OL,5,CScotland game
OL,7,FHe said: "To Steve Clarke, to Andy
OL,8,FRobertson and the Scotland national
OL,9,Fteam, I would express my warmest
OL,10,Fthanks and the thanks of everyone in
OL,11,FScotland for reaching the World Cup
OL,12,Fand then also to be able to get the
OL,13,Ffirst game as a win and to get that
OL,14,Funder their belt.
OL,26,@oD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
