PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781844476
OL,3,CWe've won against Haiti, let's beat
OL,4,CMorocco, Swinney says ahead of
OL,5,CScotland game
OL,7,F"I think that provides a really strong
OL,8,Ffoundation for the team going into the
OL,9,FMorocco game with renewed and
OL,10,Fsustained confidence, and with verve,
OL,11,Fenergy, and the ability to make sure
OL,12,Fthat we get a win when the match takes
OL,13,Fplace against Morocco."
OL,15,FThe First Minister said while Morocco
OL,16,Fwas a "much stronger team" than Haiti,
OL,17,Fthe win against the Caribbean squad
OL,18,F"establishes some pretty good
OL,19,Ffoundations for the team as they
OL,20,Fembark on the next stage of the World
OL,21,FCup campaign".
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@WO]xD@GOUxD@ZO]zD@AOU}D@MO]
