PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781844476
OL,3,CWe've won against Haiti, let's beat
OL,4,CMorocco, Swinney says ahead of
OL,5,CScotland game
OL,7,F"Yes, I think it will be a tougher
OL,8,Fgame, it'll be a tougher match," he
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"But I think we've got the confidence
OL,12,Fof having a win under our belt, and
OL,13,Fthat's more than Morocco has got as
OL,14,Fthey approach this particular match."
OL,16,FMr Swinney said he was "confident"
OL,17,Fthat Scotland could get out of the
OL,18,Fgroup stages of the World Cup, despite
OL,19,F"challenging games" ahead, including
OL,20,Ffive-time winners Brazil next week.
