OL,3,CWe've won against Haiti, let's beat
OL,4,CMorocco, Swinney says ahead of
OL,5,CScotland game
OL,7,FThe politician predicted a 2-1 win
OL,8,Fagainst Morocco but said another 1-0
OL,9,Fvictory would make him "perfectly
OL,10,Fhappy".
OL,12,FHe added: "Another win would set us in
OL,13,Fan incredible position in relation to
OL,14,Fthe World Cup, and that's what the
OL,15,Fteam should go after."
OL,17,FThe First Minister, who watched the
OL,18,Fgame in Boston last week, commended
OL,19,Fthe country's fans for "creating
OL,20,Fgoodwill" on behalf of the country.
