OL,3,CWe've won against Haiti, let's beat
OL,4,CMorocco, Swinney says ahead of
OL,5,CScotland game
OL,7,FIt comes after numerous headline-
OL,8,Fgrabbing stories from Scots in the US,
OL,9,Fincluding widespread coverage from US
OL,10,Fmedia.
OL,12,FOne story saw nuns singing "No
OL,13,FScotland, No Party" and another saw
OL,14,Fthe symbolic legalisation of haggis in
OL,15,FMassachusetts by the state's Governor,
OL,16,Fwhile Scots have been recapturing the
OL,17,FDuke of Wellington in Glasgow by
OL,18,Fplacing cones on top of statues.
OL,26,@tD@\OUuD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
