FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781844476
OL,3,CWe've won against Haiti, let's beat
OL,4,CMorocco, Swinney says ahead of
OL,5,CScotland game
OL,7,FOther outlets reported emergency
OL,8,Flevels of beer being ordered in bars
OL,9,Ffollowing visits from the Tartan Army.
OL,11,FMr Swinney said his time in Boston was
OL,12,F"a bounty of joy" with Scottish fans
OL,13,F"making a positive impression for
OL,14,FScotland".
OL,16,FHe told PA: "The Tartan Army have been
OL,17,Fextraordinary advocates and
OL,18,Fambassadors for Scotland.
OL,20,F"They've created goodwill on behalf of
OL,21,Fthe country.
OL,26,@tD@AOUtD@QO]uD@AOUvD@IO]xD@MOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
