PN,30509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1781844476
OL,3,CWe've won against Haiti, let's beat
OL,4,CMorocco, Swinney says ahead of
OL,5,CScotland game
OL,7,F"It's been lovely to watch the
OL,8,Fpositive impression that they've made.
OL,10,F"When Governor Maura Healy, the
OL,11,FGovernor of Massachusetts, came to an
OL,12,Fevent I was hosting last Friday night,
OL,13,Fshe started off her contribution by
OL,14,Fsaying, 'I think the right thing to
OL,15,Fsay is No Scotland, No Party', and she
OL,16,Fcaptured beautifully the sense of
OL,17,Fwelcome for the Scotland fans in
OL,18,FBoston, and that's something that I
OL,19,Fwill cherish forever."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOU{D@VO]
